01:24.491 --> 01:30.098
But you know, what we just heard Chris and Linda speaking about is just one tiny

01:30.818 --> 01:36.010
a part of what Skylark is wanting to do to give it home for the future.

01:36.090 --> 01:47.816
And it's worth it for me to say this, that in the same way that if you go to London, which is the capital of England, if you go there, you can't say I've seen England.

01:48.237 --> 01:50.642
You've only seen the capital of England.

01:50.818 --> 01:59.510
And you haven't seen the Lakes District, and you haven't seen Cornwall, and you haven't seen Stonehenge, and you haven't seen... You haven't seen Chelmsford.

01:59.871 --> 02:01.613
You know, there's a whole lot of things you haven't seen.

02:01.673 --> 02:19.698
The Church of Jesus Christ is the capital of the Kingdom of God, but it is not the Kingdom of God, because the things that are being done by people like Linda and Chris and so many of you that are sitting here,

02:20.034 --> 02:25.321
As soon as a person becomes a Christian, they receive a deposit of the Kingdom of Heaven.

02:25.861 --> 02:40.700
And when we receive it, we can either hang it up in the wardrobe and bring it out like a coat when we go to church or when we go to a home group or we go somewhere that's a bit spiritual, or we can make an intentional decision to carry the Kingdom of Heaven wherever we go.

02:40.720 --> 02:42.322
And that means

02:42.434 --> 02:48.780
These guys, okay, they're doing things that we can say, yes, there's a massive amount of Christianity in that.

02:48.840 --> 03:05.436
But if you're a bank manager, or if you check out Chick in Tesco, or whatever else it is that you're doing, if you intentionally make a decision to carry the kingdom of heaven with you into those places, that's the kingdom of heaven where you are.

03:05.997 --> 03:08.059
And so it's a really big deal.

03:08.139 --> 03:11.442
So I want to encourage you, yes, make a decision.

03:11.714 --> 03:21.386
to let yourself understand that Skylark Network and Skylark Church are more than connected.

03:21.526 --> 03:35.923
Like the network grew out of the church and often what happens is churches can grow out of networks, but it grew out of this vision that Maa Wiber had a long time ago when she'd never considered anything like what Skylark has become.

03:35.943 --> 03:38.386
And so I want to say, give you prayers.

03:39.298 --> 03:45.546
If you've got finances and you can see the vision of what's happening, give finances to the Sky Light Network.

03:46.087 --> 03:48.450
Give your support, give encouragement.

03:48.510 --> 04:03.090
Yesterday we had a whole lot of people, Christine and Tenney and a whole lot of other people whose names I don't know, who were just here providing the food and cleaning up and setting up and doing all the rest of it for the Sky Light Network.

04:03.591 --> 04:08.818
And you know what, you might not be the person who can do that, but you can do something and you can pray

04:08.930 --> 04:16.543
also for the leadership and the team of Skylight Network because never feel like they're all right because they're important.

04:16.964 --> 04:20.711
