04:34.114 --> 04:47.046
whether it be prayers, whether it be finance, whether it be encouragement, whether it be physical support, whatever that might be, make a decision because this is your network and it's doing something that's really remarkable.

04:48.268 --> 04:52.252
So don't take that on my time because that wasn't my time.

04:55.695 --> 05:03.122
I'm always got a bit of a problem sort of making sure I stick to the times, but hopefully I generally mostly do.

05:03.778 --> 05:31.986
So congratulations on being a hundred and we came here when Rick and I, we came here 30 years ago and that was pretty amazing but something that's been more amazing for me today has been that when I started to pray about what I could bring for this day and that was when I was in Australia, I, and the other person that's here too amazingly is Steve Crouch because he used to be our youth pastor back in the day and that's amazing and

05:32.162 --> 05:33.944
Rachel Hegetis' husband as well.

05:34.865 --> 05:40.231
I mean, there's stacks of people here that you don't even know, but for me it's kind of like a delight, you know, sorry.

05:40.912 --> 05:44.917
