06:08.316 --> 06:11.364
Now, obviously, it's not the same message, but it's the same idea.

06:11.705 --> 06:15.154
So if you are one of the very few people that were here,

06:15.234 --> 06:18.378
30 years ago, when I preached it, it'll be all right.

06:18.398 --> 06:19.820
